Checkout API

Host: https://b2b.activeshop.com.pl

Store code: B2B_PL_pl
1. Token

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/integration/customer/token
Sample request

Payload:

{
    "username": "string",
    "password": "string"
}

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
}

Response

200 Success 400 Bad request

More information: docs
Add token created to the headers for next requests

Authorization: Bearer <customer token>
2. Create a quote

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/carts/mine
Sample request

Payload: none

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Response

200 Success 400 Bad request 401 Unauthorized

More information: docs
Returned value is Your quote_id for next requests
3. Add items to cart

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/carts/mine/items
Sample request

Payload:

{
    "cartItem": {
        "sku": "string",
        "qty": 1,
        "quote_id": 1
    }
} 

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Response

200 Success 400 Bad request 401 Unauthorized
Sample response

{
  "item_id": 1,
  "sku": "string",
  "qty": 1,
  "name": "Product name",
  "price": 51,
  "product_type": "simple",
  "quote_id": "1"
}

4. Set currency
Available currencies:

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/activ-checkout/available-currencies
Sample request

Payload:

{
    "quoteId": 1,
    "addressInformation": {
        "shipping_address": {
            "region_id": 610,
            "country_id": "PL",
            "street": [
                "Graniczna",
                "8b",
                "bud. DC2A"
            ],
            "postcode": "54-610",
            "city": "Wrocław",
            "firstname": "Jan",
            "lastname": "Kowalski",
            "company": "Firma",
            "telephone": "987654321"
        },
        "shipping_carrier_code": "dhl_poland",
        "shipping_method_code": "dhl_poland"
    }
}

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Response

200 Success 400 Bad request 401 Unauthorized
Sample response

[
    "EUR",
    "PLN"
]

Set currency:

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/activ-checkout/set-currency
Sample request

Payload:

{
    "currencyCode": "EUR"
}

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Response

200 Success 400 Bad request 401 Unauthorized
Sample response

Totals for current quote. More information: docs
5. Shipping methods
Fetching country and region ids:

GET <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/directory/countries

More information: docs
