Details of the shipment can be found in the extension_attributes.shipping_calculation_result fields
Field 	Type 	Description
standard_volume_amount 	float 	Total volume of standard packages
oversized_volume_amount 	float 	Total volume of oversized packages
weight_amount 	float 	Total weight of the shipment
standard_pallet_qty 	int 	Number of standard pallets required for the shipment
oversized_pallet_qty 	int 	Number of oversized pallets required for the shipment
cartons_qty 	int 	Number of cartons in the shipment
fragile_products_qty 	int 	Number of fragile products in the shipment
non_standard_products 	array 	List of SKUs of products that require non-standard handling
non_standard_products_qty 	int 	Total number of non-standard products
7. Set payment

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/carts/mine/set-payment-information

Payload:

{
    "cartId": 1,
    "paymentMethod": {
        "method": "banktransfer"
    }
}

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Response

200 Success 401 Unauthorized
8. Attachments

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/activ-checkout/attachments/uploadAttachment

Payload:

{
    "filename": "filename.pdf",
    "base64Content": "base64 encoded content of PDF file"
}

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Sample response

4 - id of attachment

GET <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/activ-checkout/attachments/list Payload: none

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Sample response:

[
    {
        "attachment_id": 7,
        "filename": "file1.pdf"
    },
    {
        "attachment_id": 8,
        "filename": "file2.pdf"
    }
]

DELETE <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/activ-checkout/attachments/removeAllAttachments

Payload: none

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Sample response:

true
9. Set parameters

POST <host>/rest/<store_code>/V1/activ-checkout/synchronizeQuoteParams
Sample request

Payload:

{
    "params":
    {
        "comment": "Order comment",
        "order_type": "own"
    }
}

order_type can be own or dropshipping

Headers:

{
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer <customer token>"
}

Response

200 Success 401 Unauthorized

Response contains agreements information.
Sample response

[
    {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Regulamin",
        "content": "Potwierdzam, że zapoznałem/am się z treść regulaminu dostępną w zakładce <a style="font-weight: bold;color: #f00;" target="_blank" href="/regulamin">Regulamin Sklepu</a> lub pod adresem https://activeshop.com.pl/regulamin i akceptuje go w pełni.",
        "step": "",
        "checkbox_text": "Akceptuje regulamin zakupów",
        "is_required": true,
        "is_selected": false
    },
    {
        "id": 3,
        "name": "Rodo",
        "content": "Oświadczam, że wyrażam zgodę na przetwarzanie moich danych osobowych zgodnie z Rozporządzeniem Parlamentu Europejskiego i Rady (UE) 2016/679 z dnia 27 kwietnia 2016 r. w sprawie ochrony osób fizycznych w związku z przetwarzaniem danych osobowych i w sprawie swobodnego przepływu takich danych oraz uchylenia dyrektywy 95/46/WE",
        "step": "",
        "checkbox_text": "Akceptuje regulamin przetwarzania danych osobowych",
